 Ballavpurer Roopkatha

 With loads of humour and witty repartees, the Nandipat production exposes the pompousness and false grandeur of the wealthy landed gentry. The play by Badal Sircar is directed by Prakash Bhattacharya.

Catch it at Madhusudan Mancha, 6.30 pm, October 

22

 Ho Sakta Hai Do Aadmi Do Kursiyaan

 Written and directed by Vinay Sharma, the play comprises 14 short and apparently unconnected scenes. The theme of human relationships in an urban milieu binds them together.

 Catch it at Padatik Little Theatre, 7 pm, October 22




